irst=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-07-13|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715151636/http://deadline.com/2016/07/miss-sloane-jessica-chastain-december-release-date-1201786282/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後改至2016年11月25日[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=misssloane.htm|title=Miss Sloane|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020040612/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=misssloane.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《攻敵必救》獲得的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於131條評論，新鮮度71%，平均得分6.5／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_sloane/|title=Miss Sloane (2016)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2016-01-24|archive-date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331162741/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_sloane|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上獲得63分，代表「整體正面的評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/miss-sloane|title=Miss Sloane|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-12-28|archive-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229042425/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/miss-sloane|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在[[北美|北美]]，《攻敵必救》與《[[聖誕搞轟趴|聖誕搞轟趴]]》、《{{le|愛情捲土重來|The Bounce Back}}》及廣泛上映的《[[迷離字戀|迷離字戀]]》共同上映競爭，估計能從首週末獲得200萬至400萬美元的票房。美國首週末票房僅180萬美元，排名當週第十一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/12/11/weekend-box-office-office-christmas-party-sets-record-miss-sloane-bombs/ |title=Weekend Box Office: 'Office Christmas Party' Sets Record, 'Miss Sloane' Bombs |work=Forbes |date=2016-11-14 |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archive-date=2016-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212014016/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/12/11/weekend-box-office-office-christmas-party-sets-record-miss-sloane-bombs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《攻敵必救》的最終票房總計370萬美元，對比預算的1300萬美元來說，表現不佳<ref name=numbers/>。

